# Final check for all classes and properties.
All concrete classes have instances.
All object properties have been used to link entities, respecting domain/range.
All datatype properties have been used to add literals, respecting xsd:type.
SKOS concepts are defined and used.
Entities are grouped and have rdfs:label and rdfs:comment.
The graph is reasonably large and interconnected.
No ldp prefix in the generated data.
No punctuation at the start of statements.
All literals are correctly formatted with ^^xsd:type.
All prefixes are declared.
